@page "/orders"
@attribute [Authorize(Roles = "admin")]
@inject GatewayClient Gateway

<h1>Orders</h1>
<p style="color:#6b7280;">Order management reads through the gateway; per-order detail (payment state, per-line
fulfillment, tickets) is added as those read endpoints land.</p>
<p>Use the <a href="/ledger">Ledger</a> and <a href="/rmas">RMA queue</a> for money operations.</p>
